{"tid":996612,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[人生] 如果係你，應該揀邊樣？","createTime":"2019-01-26T12:12:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-27T01:16:17.000Z","uid":100700,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b5f61f0d795061e564ddbdef220fa138263d7ac0","tid":996612,"uid":100700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T12:12:28.000Z","msg":"自從前排上網睇到秋赤音嘅youtube channel，自畫mv加作曲，唱歌又勁，就想之後都學佢咁做。<br />\n本身自己識識畫野、photoshop同後製剪片等等，為左增強呢方面嘅技能同諗頭，就見左份designer嘅工。不過因為規模細既原因，份工有可能經常性OT。亦因為我音樂channel仲處於無咩人知既狀態，呢份工有可能令音樂channel既營運方面出現問題，好難每日出一個post去保持exposure，更何況要高質。<br />\n所以，問題就黎。如果收到offer，俾著係你會點揀？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 做，post重質不重量，係高質自然會有人發現，更何況未試過點知唔可以兩邊兼顧。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：唔做，時間有限，第時兩頭唔到岸就dum春。<br />\n<br />\n求意見。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"244f6db9bba0630ee63faa98cba9c88824990442","tid":996612,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T12:13:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"37fb0153f23c2b52bc8b2bbec5a36239348a97c1","tid":996612,"uid":100700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T12:14:46.000Z","msg":"帶番個頭盔先，其實我啲音樂去到見得人仲差幾皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1635e5b209139e306d69166aeb617faef26b868f","tid":996612,"uid":100700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"244f6db9bba0630ee63faa98cba9c88824990442","tid":996612,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T12:13:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T12:32:56.000Z","msg":"撚同𨶙唔識分？"},{"pid":"46e19ebfb3ee10f0221b29f33c5aed3850a53faa","tid":996612,"uid":81340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T12:34:25.000Z","msg":"人生只係幾十年, 想做就做"},{"pid":"d551c23ecdd9b4b89e557a778f31e8759c09e3ad","tid":996612,"uid":100700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T12:46:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fd005625d3017f184598d7afd79b360aa97b0c6e","tid":996612,"uid":39728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T01:09:17.000Z","msg":"屌 撳錯負皮"},{"pid":"913d8501177c2d209f5164d89e14195ca173c0fa","tid":996612,"uid":39728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T01:16:17.000Z","msg":"重質不重量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得可以試下兩邊都同時進行<br />\n其實我都有呢個問題要面對<br />\n以前份工體力勞動多 返到去做唔到其他嘢<br />\n而家轉咗工變咗精神上攰<br />\n未適應返工嗰邊變咗又係無辦法返去就練畫<br />\n所以你反而可能要諗下<br />\n接咗offer初期未必可以兼顧<br />\n但唔好放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好嘅作品係有凝聚力<br />\n觀眾會願意等<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}